-- Mauritius Seeks Advisers for 100 Megawatt Power Plant
-- B y   K a m l e s h   B h u c k o r y
-- 2012-06-05T14:37:51Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-05/mauritius-seeks-advisers-for-100-megawatt-power-plant.html
Mauritius is seeking advisers for a
proposed tender to build a 100-megawatt coal-fired power plant,
the  Finance Ministry  said.  The African Development Bank is assisting Mauritius, the
country said in a statement published in the Port Louis-based le
Mauricien newspaper today, without being more specific.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Kamlesh Bhuckory in Port Louis at 
 kbhuckory@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Antony Sguazzin at 
 asguazzin@bloomberg.net  